{"tid":1026096,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[贏] 金融時報：英國政府自認可降低使用華為設備風險","createTime":"2019-02-17T23:53:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T00:54:21.000Z","uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"628aaa777aa9e15906a45519e2a3a1cc67dcf76a","tid":1026096,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T23:53:26.000Z","msg":"金融時報：英國政府自認可降低使用華為設備風險<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201902180007.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F201902180007.aspx&d=8lKb2kYWDOzPE5G8cc2TgHf7N2ZoUQ5IAXdO3fO0pAc%3D&h=f40661bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201902180007.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n（中央社倫敦17日綜合外電報導）英國「金融時報」（Financial Times）今天引述消息人士報導，英國政府已做出結論，認為他們可以降低使用中國電信巨擘華為公司（Huawei）5G網路設備所帶來的風險。<br />\n<br />\n報導引述熟悉英國國家網路安全中心（NCSC）決策的2名消息人士說法，其中一位消息人指出，英國當局做出的結論將對歐洲各國領袖「形成重大影響」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">消息人士告訴金融時報：「其他國家可以提出這樣的論點，即是假設英國當局有信心降低國家安全威脅，那他們也可以向民眾和美國政府保證，他們會謹慎行事，並繼續允許國內電信服務供應商使用中國零件，只要他們採取英國建議的各種防範措施。」</span><br />\n<br />\n路透社報導，美國政府曾指控，華為和中國網路設備公司中興通訊（ZTE）聽從中國政府的命令運作。<br />\n<br />\n美國政府還指控，華為和中興通訊的設備可用來監視美國民眾，但華為再三否認這些指控。"},{"pid":"31718e4c4d58ec41d9a53cab03283136e9903b45","tid":1026096,"uid":41245,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T00:36:17.000Z","msg":"噏乜<br />\n引消息人士都講到1999噉報嚟做乜柒"},{"pid":"2433ebc8fb07c0c95be3c230e533dd9f3087a5bc","tid":1026096,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T00:38:42.000Z","msg":"今早tvb 新聞吹咗啦"},{"pid":"627b47f6c366f3e77d76c53498166533aa18ffe5","tid":1026096,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T00:42:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"784e004fcc6a962176f96d34ce8a7d4f8d065c9a","tid":1026096,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T00:42:20.000Z","msg":"據奧地利《標準報》網站2月13日報導，阿爾諾爾德納說：&ldquo;人們不應該把地緣政治討論與技術討論混為一談。&rdquo;他說，大多數歐洲電信運營商都會與華為合作，例如奧地利電信公司。迄今為止該公司是和諾基亞公司擴建大部分奧地利移動通信網絡和光纖網絡的。阿爾諾爾德納說：&ldquo;我們沒有計劃改變與華為現有的合作，我們不排除華為。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n奧地利《標準報》網站稱，值得注意的是，現在哪些大炮被架起來。美國國務卿邁克&middot;蓬佩奧警告說，出於安全政治原因，不要把5G移動網絡的建設委託給中國網絡設備供應商華為公司，因為該公司與北京關係密切，可以提供自己的設備或手機進行&ldquo;間諜&rdquo;活動。<br />\n<br />\n　　文章指出，蓬佩奧沒有為這些指控提供證據。因此美國人在歐洲也沒有得到太多支持。此外，華為通常比競爭對手更便宜。"},{"pid":"4fe8da58b24414a8930600ef8bf8da152a1b922c","tid":1026096,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T00:46:31.000Z","msg":"歷史不斷重演，英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.history.com/.image/ar_16:9%2Cc_fill%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cg_faces:center%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_768/MTU3OTIzNjYwOTQyNTUwNjc0/chamberlain-declares-peace-for-our-time-75-years-agos-featured-photo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.history.com%2F.image%2Far_16%3A9%252Cc_fill%252Ccs_srgb%252Cfl_progressive%252Cg_faces%3Acenter%252Cq_auto%3Agood%252Cw_768%2FMTU3OTIzNjYwOTQyNTUwNjc0%2Fchamberlain-declares-peace-for-our-time-75-years-agos-featured-photo.jpg&h=421a7eb3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ec3f82143382a12dc14edd938f8b4e3e78d0a4c","tid":1026096,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fe8da58b24414a8930600ef8bf8da152a1b922c","tid":1026096,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T00:46:31.000Z","msg":"歷史不斷重演，英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.history.com/.image/ar_16:9%2Cc_fill%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cg_faces:center%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_768/MTU3OTIzNjYwOTQyNTUwNjc0/chamberlain-declares-peace-for-our-time-75-years-agos-featured-photo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.history.com%2F.image%2Far_16%3A9%252Cc_fill%252Ccs_srgb%252Cfl_progressive%252Cg_faces%3Acenter%252Cq_auto%3Agood%252Cw_768%2FMTU3OTIzNjYwOTQyNTUwNjc0%2Fchambe